{"tid":33342,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哥迪奧拿：曼城要輸番場","createTime":"2016-12-10T17:41:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-15T15:16:18.000Z","uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"352a17ad74e751c56ce5c31ba159c68a56833aba","tid":33342,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T17:41:55.000Z","msg":"曼城領隊哥迪奧拿認為現在一切太順利，只要有一場敗仗一切就會改變，並笑說希望這場敗仗快點來到。<br />\n<br />\n哥迪奧拿帶領曼城開季8戰全勝，哥帥亦明白大家的期望，更加明白如果一輸，會發生甚麼情況。<br />\n<br />\n被問到球員連場征戰會否在體力上有問題，哥帥就表示球員在贏波後沒有感到疲憊，並認為一切不安的言論將會影響軍心。<br />\n<br />\n「你有否看過贏4:0之後球員會覺得累?我從沒見過，當贏波時你會覺得更加舒服，士氣亦會提高。我們需要贏出比賽搶分，但我更希望可以輸一場‥&hellip;當然只是說笑，但這樣的確可減壓力。」<br />\n<br />\n「最近我聽到很多對不同領隊的批評，但這並不公平，現在只踢了5場聯賽，如果我的球隊輸波，我一定是最清楚原因的一個。」<br />\n<br />\n哥狗如你所願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e03d53f81017e454d0895a2cc4178cd502f56e4","tid":33342,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T17:50:53.000Z","msg":"3:0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec75d1d4c342d2571354f4f72733dcc5ac54d46","tid":33342,"uid":59753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T18:07:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f238c20fd39c58daf849300c4593c9c34b5138d","tid":33342,"uid":5005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T18:15:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2ae67824696cc8fe266cf59a144da807eacb16","tid":33342,"uid":46507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T18:21:06.000Z","msg":"唔知仲要bin多幾多場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9584d75bd41c3d1001dd25bc92b50fad2b6a3363","tid":33342,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-